OL,3,CJury considers verdict in PC murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FA jury has retired to consider
OL,7,Fverdicts in the trial of a man accused
OL,8,Fof murdering a police officer by
OL,9,Fplanning the armed robbery in which
OL,10,Fshe was killed.
OL,12,FPiran Ditta Khan is alleged to be the
OL,13,Fmastermind behind a raid at family-run
OL,14,FUniversal Express travel agents in
OL,15,FNovember 2005.
OL,17,FPC Sharon Beshenivsky, 38, was shot on
OL,18,Fher youngest daughter's fourth
OL,19,Fbirthday as she arrived at the robbery
OL,20,Fon Morley Street, Bradford. She died
OL,21,Ffrom her injuries.
