OL,6,FHer colleague Pc Teresa Milburn was
OL,7,Fseriously injured after being shot by
OL,8,Fthe gunman ` one of three armed men
OL,9,Fwho had just carried out the robbery
OL,10,Fand fled the scene with around #5,400
OL,11,Fin cash.
OL,13,FProsecutors claim Khan, 75, was the
OL,14,Fgroup's ringleader and played a
OL,15,F"pivotal" role in planning the raid
OL,16,Fand giving instructions to the others.
OL,18,FThey say this makes him guilty of PC
OL,19,FBeshenivsky's murder "as surely as if
OL,20,Fhe had pulled the trigger himself".
