OL,3,CJury considers verdict in PC murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FJurors have heard Khan was in a
OL,7,Flookout car eating sandwiches with
OL,8,Fanother of the robbers, Hassan Razzaq,
OL,9,Fwhile the raid was being carried out.
OL,11,FProsecutors say he was the only one of
OL,12,Fthe group who was familiar with
OL,13,FUniversal Express and had been using
OL,14,Fthe business for years to transfer
OL,15,Fmoney to family in Pakistan.
OL,17,FKhan denies knowing that a robbery was
OL,18,Fgoing to be committed, or that weapons
OL,19,Fwere going to be taken to Universal
OL,20,FExpress that day.
