OL,6,FHe has claimed the motive for the
OL,7,Frobbery was that the business's owner,
OL,8,FMohammad Yousaf, owed him #12,000, and
OL,9,Fthat debt collector Razzaq offered to
OL,10,Fget his money back when the pair met
OL,11,Fthrough a business associate.
OL,13,FKhan told Leeds Crown Court he thought
OL,14,Fthe men Razzaq sent would simply
OL,15,F"intimidate" the staff or, at most,
OL,16,F"slap" them.
