OL,6,FThe judge, Mr Justice Hilliard, told
OL,7,Fjurors the defendant would be guilty
OL,8,Fof murder if they were sure he
OL,9,F"intentionally encouraged the primary
OL,10,Frobbers to take part (...) and
OL,11,Fintended serious harm should be
OL,12,Fcaused, if necessary, to carry out the
OL,13,Frobbery and escape with the proceeds".
OL,15,FHe sent the jury out to consider its
OL,16,Fverdicts at just before 3.30pm on
OL,17,FWednesday.
OL,19,FThe court has heard Khan is the last
OL,20,Fof the seven men involved in the
OL,21,Frobbery to face trial.
