OL,6,FHe flew to Pakistan two months after
OL,7,FPC Beshenivsky's death and remained
OL,8,Fthere before being arrested by
OL,9,FPakistani authorities in 2020 and
OL,10,Fextradited to the UK last year, jurors
OL,11,Fwere told.
OL,13,FThe other members of the group have
OL,14,Fbeen convicted of offences including
OL,15,Fmurder, manslaughter, robbery and
OL,16,Ffirearms offences.
OL,18,FKhan denies murder, two counts of
OL,19,Fpossession of a firearm with intent to
OL,20,Fendanger life and two counts of
OL,21,Fpossession of a prohibited weapon.
